article.description: — Jaylen Forbes had a career-high 21 points as Tulane beat Grambling State 77-65 on Saturday.
article.headline: Forbes scores 21 to carry Tulane over Grambling State 77-65
article.linkText: Forbes scores 21 to carry Tulane over Grambling State 77-65
article.story: NEW ORLEANS -- — Jaylen Forbes had a career-high 21 points as Tulane beat Grambling State 77-65 on Saturday. Gabe Watson had 18 points for Tulane (5-1). Jordan Walker added 11 points. Prince Moss had 18 points for the Tigers (2-4). Cameron Christon added 16 points and nine rebounds. Kelton Edwards had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
